ITK5DQ7AE4KM326AE6BB32UB.description:
Dive into a bowl of freshness with our new Crunch Salad, a delightful medley of vibrant ingredients designed to tantalize your taste buds. This nutritious salad features a crisp blend of kale, carrots, red onion, and cabbage, all topped with creamy feta cheese. Drizzled with our signature house-made vinaigrette dressing, every bite is a burst of flavor and crunch.

Customize your Crunch Salad with our premium protein options: choose from free-run chicken, succulent prawns, organic tofu, or soy-free tofu. Protein is cooked on our cast iron grill in our famous scratch made Lemon Grass Ginger Sauce

For an extra health boost, add beets for just $0.50.

Perfect for a healthy lunch or a light dinner, the Crunch Salad is your go-to choice for a delicious and wholesome meal.
